welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Northfield, a charming city nestled in the heart of the United States. Known for its rich history and picturesque scenery, we invite you to explore all that Northfield has to offer and make unforgettable memories during your visit."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Municipal Airport offers a variety of amenities and services for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: For those flying on private jets, there is a separate terminal with luxurious lounges and concierge services.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Minneapolis - St. Paul International Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal at Minneapolis - St. Paul International Airport, primarily serving low-cost carriers and regional flights.

wifi.note: Free Wi-Fi is available throughout the airport.
